### 测试API接口 (可以在VS Code的REST Client扩展中使用)

### 1. 查询所有记录
GET http://localhost:5000/api/details

###

### 2. 新增一条记录
POST http://localhost:5000/api/details
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "test123",
  "type": "expense",
  "category": "测试",
  "amount": 100.50,
  "date": "2025-11-10",
  "note": "这是一条测试记录"
}

###

### 3. 更新记录
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/details/test123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "income",
  "category": "测试收入",
  "amount": 200.00,
  "date": "2025-11-10",
  "note": "更新后的测试记录"
}

###

### 4. 删除指定记录
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/details/test123

###

### 5. 清空所有记录（谨慎使用！）
# DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/details

###


